                        Many industries. Countless products. One focus.
                    
 
 



                        At first glance, Koch companies might look curiously unrelated. After all, they stretch from the fibers of fashion to the rugged world of ranching. When you look deeper, there’s a common thread that ties them together. It’s a desire to keep improving the products that meet your basic needs every single day.
                    



                                More than
                            

                                120,000
                            

                                employees in 60 countries worldwide
                            



                                More than
                            

                                1,200
                            

                                excellence awards since 2009
                            


Historically
                            

                                90%
                            

                                of earnings reinvested into the company
                            


 
 






Flint Hills Resources



                                By responsibly harnessing natural resources and innovation, our modern way of life just keeps getting better. From next-generation fuels to essential chemical components, we work tirelessly to power, and empower, us all.
                            

                                Learn More
                            

 
 





Georgia-Pacific



                                Our handiwork includes everyday items such as plywood and lumber, Quilted Northern® tissue and Brawny® towels, Dixie® cups and more.
                            

                                Learn More
                            

 
 





Guardian Industries



                                We make high-performance glass and automotive trim for customers around the world — while helping supply building materials across America.
                            

                                Learn More
                            

 
 





INVISTA



                                You might know our STAINMASTER® carpet, and LYCRA® fiber for clothing. We also make materials for bedding, air bags, engines, backpacks and the list goes on and on. 
                            

                                Learn More
                            

 
 





Molex



                                Electronics inspire advancements in communication, medical equipment, transportation, appliances and more. We make the connecting components that bring it all to life. 
                            

                                Learn More
                            

 
 





Koch Ag & Energy Solutions



                                We provide fertilizer products that help farmers nourish crops responsibly, to put more food on tables. We’re also a reliable source for gas and electricity that energizes the nation.
                            

                                Learn More
                            

 
 





Koch Chemical Technology Group



                                From filtration technologies that increase the world’s supply of clean water, to pollution control equipment for manufacturers, our products stand up for the environment.
                            

                                Learn More
                            

 
 





Koch Minerals



                                Industries depend on commodity resources worldwide to make products that you use every day. We market and trade more than 40 million tons of these materials annually.
                            

                                Learn More
                            

 
 





Koch Pipeline



                                Before there’s fuel at the gas station, someone has to safely move it along the way. We operate about 4,000 miles of petroleum product pipelines to make that happen.
                            

                                Learn More
                            

 
 





Koch Supply & Trading



                                Global trading of energy commodities and metals takes knowledge and attention to detail. We’ve been applying both for decades to manage pricing, risks and logistics.
                            

                                Learn More
                            

 
 





Matador Cattle Company



                                Some Koch employees literally hop back in the saddle each morning. Our cattle ranches in Montana, Kansas and Texas cover 460,000 acres.
                            

                                Learn More
                            

 
 





Opportunity knocks.
Discover a career that’s perfect for you among our diverse, global companies.

