                                    Koch Membrane Systems
                                


 




                                    Helping Solve the Global Water Crisis 
                                

                                    Manny Singh experienced the global water crisis firsthand when he was child. Today at Koch, he’s helping solve it one city at a time.
                                







                                    Alexis
                                

                                  Sales Team Leader  
                                


 
 



                                    "My boss saw how much happier I was and how much more fulfilled I was every day. He really encouraged me to [pursue personal passions]."
                                




 




                            Benefits
                        

                            Our people are our greatest and most important resource. That's why we support the personal and professional health and development of our employees – by providing each with insurance, retirement benefits, educational assistance and paid time off. 
                        

                            Specific benefits vary by company.
                        


 


