                                    Respecting the great outdoors, Flint Hills Resources has reduced refinery emissions by 69 percent since 1997 and teamed up with environmental ally Ducks Unlimited.
                                

 
 

 






                                    Cleaner, Safer Combustion
                                

                                    Read Story
                                
 
 



                                    At our John Zink Hamworthy Combustion test center, we create cleaner combustion while increasing safety, reducing energy use and minimizing our eco footprint.
                                

 
 




                                    John’s Mission
                                

